      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers practical transportation at an accessible price. An excellent fit for a value-focused buyer, commuter, or project-minded owner, it delivers solid utility and a straightforward ownership proposition. Priced to reflect its condition while still presenting real everyday usefulness, this is a great chance to secure dependable basic transportation without stretching your budget.",
